snippet.title: MSX-21 - MSX Gameplay
snippet.description:
Released in 1983 by ASCII Corporation in Japan, this is a simple simulation of Blackjack and Poker for the MSX. The video footage is mainly focused on the main Blackjack portion. Its European release was handled by Panasonic.

#msx #blackjack #poker #retrogames #retrogaming #msx21
